questionTemplate.question: The Truth must dazzle gradually Or every man be blind.
Heroism feels and never reasons, and therefore is always right. (NPS)
The young are generally full of revolt, and are often pretty revolting about it.
The actions of men are the best interpreters of their thoughts.

values.value: We live in a fantasy world, a world of illusion. The great task in life is to find reality.
If you want your neighbor to know what the Christ spirit will do for him, let him see what it has done for you.
Every rod or staff of empire is truly crooked at the top.
I am extraordinarily patient provided I get my own way in the end.

If you want your neighbor to know what the Christ spirit will doa for him, let him see what it has done for you.
